OL,5, NHS bosses are increasingly paying     
OL,6, premium rates for agency staff to plug 
OL,7, holes in rotas, the BBC has found.     
OL,9,FSpending in this area rose by 20% last 
OL,10,Fyear to hit #3bn in England.           
OL,12,FFor many shifts, bosses have been so   
OL,13,Fshort-staffed they have been willing to
OL,14,Fbreach the government pay caps for     
OL,15,Fthese agency workers, most of whom are 
OL,16,Fdoctors and nurses.                    
OL,18,FSeparate data supplied by Labour showed
OL,19,Fsome NHS trusts had paid as much as    
OL,20,F#2,500 to nurses to fill shifts.       
